Devs still make new partners, but that does not make the project a success. It can only be successful if this token is also easily tradable on the market. But also doing more marketing is not a bad thing. . Now we have done something wrong. Because in the Cryptoworld everything is about speculations and news that determines the course. Now they are doing everything while they are placed on 1 exchange which was also free for listing where there is no trade volume at all.  The price you see only further collapse, even with news updates. If they have spent a few pennies for placement on hitbtc then the price would have been much better with the updates they have released.     New partners Where can you pay with VST tokens? Now we will briefly acquaint you with each participant of a marketplace Vestarin, who has joined upon completion of ICO:  1. ECO Cars www.ecocars.com.ua ‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääone of the largest dealers of electric vehicles in Ukraine with representations in Kyiv, Odesa, and Lviv. Now it is possible to buy electric vehicles in ECO Cars for VST.  2. Toka www.toka.energy - the first national network of charging stations for the electric vehicles in Ukraine. With Vestarin platform it is possible not only to buy electric cars but also to pay their charging!  3. Bls  www.bls.ua‚Äì the car rental company. Our partner offers not only car rent, but also used cars sale and leasing programs. Now all this is available for VST!  4. Yabloko https://yabloko.studio/ ‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääweb-design studio. Owners of our tokens have an opportunity to use a full range of services in web-design, paying off with VST. Web development of different level of complexity, start of new brands and re-branding, researches in the field of User Experience (UX), development of content strategy for social media and conducting campaigns on social networks. All these services can be ordered from Yabloko for Vestarin system tokens now.  5. VipSky  http://vipsky.com.ua/‚Ää ‚Äî‚Ääthe charter aircraft company providing a full complex of services in business aircraft. Here it is possible not only to order a VIP-charter flight but even to rent the helicopter for unforgettable flights. With Vestarin and VipSky flights for tokens become a reality!  6. 103air http://103air.com.ua/‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääair ambulance. The company specializes in the organization of personal air transportation of the patients, who need the emergency medical care.  7. Goose Gastro Pub https://www.facebook.com/GooseGastroPub/  ‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääthe pub for a good rest. Tasty food, excellent drinks‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääall this is available for VST.  8. Marani‚Ää https://www.facebook.com/marani.vinnytsya/ ‚Äî‚Äärestaurant not only to eat but also to communicate in the cozy atmosphere. It is the restaurant of Georgian cuisine and wine. Enjoy distinguished drinks and tasty refined dishes for VST!  9. Shishka https://www.facebook.com/Shishka61/ ‚Ää‚Äî‚Äähookah bar. A cozy place with the rich menu of European cuisine and a wide choice of hookah tobacco‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääup to 700 types! All this can be got for our tokens.  10. Regenschirm https://www.facebook.com/regenschirmclub/‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääbar and dancing night club. The beautiful place where it is possible not only to have a rest with a cocktail but also to dump freight of the working day on a dance floor. Pay off with VST and have a rest with pleasure.  We are not going to stop. We continue to establish relations with the most different companies from the different countries. It is only the beginning! Soon more goods and services will become available for our token‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääbe aware and don‚Äôt miss our updates in social networks.  Together we will make marketplace Vestarin more convenient and scaled!

Author: Kirilp
Title: [ANN]VESTARINüöÄICO is LIVE |Marketplace of goods and services for cryptocurrency
Body: Vestarin: an update from developers    Dear friends, community and all, who are interested in the Vestarin project! We want to share with you the latest news and the important announcement‚Ää‚Äî‚Äärelease of the new functions is on the way!  What we are busy now with At first, about the current situation. Now we work on back-end functionality of a mobile application of the platform. Plus, the front-end part of the desktop version is ready. Also, our team continues to involve new partners to the Vestarin ecosystem, that could be seen in social networks.  What to wait for in the near future? About the future important events, along with completion of the separate elements of the platform, we prepare for the release of the first sections of the Vestarin system. The release of the first functionality will take place very soon: within two weeks. We plan to start the sections Registration, Professionals, Chat, Profile, News and ICO.  Of course, the sections News and ICO still demand to fill by content, it will take some time. But there will be ready sections with qualitative information and thematic materials from the world of ICO projects, the fintech-industry and blockchain technologies.  Vestarin becomes one more step closer to the fully working multipurpose platform.  To the community We want to thank all who support our project and help to achieve the goal. We need your support now. We urge all VST token-holders to be patient. Soon you will be able to estimate functionality of Vestarin and to be convinced, that we really make all efforts, creating for you a really qualitative product.  Don‚Äôt follow the token-hunters or beginners, who are interested in the token, not in the platform with a full-fledged turn of tokens. It is an extremely short-sighted approach. We will remind, cryptocurrencies with the serious turnover are accepted by the exchanges with much more loyal conditions‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääthis way is longer, but it is more reliable.  Token-hunters, exchange speculators and beginners panic consciously or on ignorance, not up to the end understanding how the long-term investments work. Some people want to get rid of tokens as soon as possible, bringing its price down, thus, having framed the community and our team of developers. This is an unfair behavior, but we don‚Äôt ignore even their interests‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääjust ask to wait. Everything is good in its season!  International cryptocurrency marketplace is not even an online store, which development takes many months‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääit is much more difficult and more large-scale. It is impossible to build a qualitative digital product in one month, therefore, we urge you to be patient for the sake of future achievements. Much thanks to those, who understand it and support the team!  In fact, we are the first and we move forward at own risk. There are no ready decisions for the creation of the multipurpose crypto‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääplatform, but our experts are firmly convinced of the course and know how to achieve goals. Token not end in itself, but only an ecosystem element, important, however not only.  We create everything have from scratch and have already achieved quite good results in development. At the same time, we develop the mobile and desktop application version, we continue to look for and successfully find new partners for a marketplace of the platform. In our opinion, it is a very good speed for a so young startup. Our team doesn‚Äôt look for a momentary hype but tries to create a really working and necessary product, that will give a token a stable liquidity and provide its further growth.  Vestarin doesn‚Äôt intend to stop and will move forward only, contrary to all ill-wishers and skeptics! The future of the fintech-industry is ours! https://medium.com/@vestarin/vestarin-an-update-from-developers-e48b41678236

Author: eren0x
Title: [ANN]VESTARINüöÄICO is LIVE |Marketplace of goods and services for cryptocurrency
Body: Vestarin platform is a marketplace for goods and services, platform for cryptonetworking. Crypto world is in the infancy of its development and today it is not brought up to full strength. However, there is still no way to do everyday purchases, paying with crypto currency. For example, order a game console or TV, eat at a restaurant, pay maid service in crypto currency. It's about the daily expenses and the opportunity to spend the crypto currency without bringing it to fiat money. Yhey decided to fill the existing gaps, and create what is missing. Vestarin is a platform based on a mobile application that will allow you to make daily purchases, paying with crypto currency.

However we cannot disclose any details at the moment, due to non disclosure agreements.

Body: Vestarin outpaces the world trends  So-called ‚ÄòMarch to acknowledge the cryptocurrencies‚Äô already spread around the world! Currently it is a global trend - governments all around the world determine their position in regard of digital coins, gradually legalizing them everywhere. Striking example relate to the news spread all over the world that the first national cryptocurrency Venezuelan Petro had collected an impressive USD 5 billion on the presale! This result is a huge step in appreciation of true potential of cryptocurrencies as a financial tool. Other countries will definitely act in this way to experience it. Another country of Latin America, Mexico, went another way. The Mexican parliament has adopted a law on digital coins regulating having defined their legal status as a commodity. Despite the fact that cryptocurrencies have already been legalized in another form, different from Venezuela, Japan and Germany, it is still a big plus and major asset for crypto industry. Positive decisions on cryptocurrencies legal status have already been made by a number of countries, and this tendency gains momentum. Gradual recognition of cryptocurrencies ensures its increasing usage as a means of payment. Author: crevbi
Title: [ANN]VESTARINüöÄICO is LIVE |Marketplace of goods and services for cryptocurrency
Body: Vestarin will help you understand everything about cryptocurrencies The popularity of the blockchain and cryptocurrencies does not lessen, but common people still do not understand the need and essence of it. To help correct this, some countries have launched their own educational projects at the national level. So, for example, the government of Venezuela has opened a training center to teach those interested to work with cryptocurrency, mining and also the basics of the economy of this sphere.  Our Vestarin team follows these trends. Our goal is to help and train all users on the planet to understand everything that needs to be known about the crypto- industry. For this purpose we will be posting articles with the training cases on how businesses, developers and buyers can work with our platform. It is necessary to experience all the potential of our platform and cryptocurrencies as a means of payment.  https://www.facebook.com/vestarin.io/photos/a.173373966577245.1073741828.173221989925776/212306146017360/?type=3&theater

Author: Jekwizor
Title: [ANN]VESTARINüöÄICO is LIVE |Marketplace of goods and services for cryptocurrency
Body: Vestarin has opened preliminary registration for business More and more people start using cryptocurrency as digital money is sometimes more productive than fiat money. It challenges business to broaden payments reception format according to current trends. Cryptocurrencies is an effective tool which will make your business up-to-date, fast and convenient. To achieve it we are developing our Vestarin platform. We are happy to announce the start of Business pre- registration for those who are ready to keep step in due course and accept cryptocurrency as payment. We are working on a pilot database of contacts, and we will apply first and foremost those who register now. We are happy to inform you that upon preliminary registration allocating your Business on the platform is free of charge. The preliminary registration does not collect data on goods or services, however, it gives the opportunity for the business to define its own niche.   https://www.facebook.com/vestarin.io/photos/a.173373966577245.1073741828.173221989925776/211697032744938/?type=3&theater

Author: Kirilp
Title: [ANN]VESTARINüöÄICO is LIVE |Marketplace of goods and services for cryptocurrency
Body: Meet the Boss ‚Äì Exclusive Interview with Vestarin CEO Said Radzhabov  magine a world where all you had to do, to buy anything, hire anyone, launch a business, invest or learn about cryptocurrency, was to pay a few cyber coins with the click of a button.  Imagine being able to raise funds for your next venture by just putting out a team project outline, and being able to pay all your team members with the same cryptocurrency.  Imagine no more. Vestarin is a blockchained platform with its own ETH-based cryptocurrency connecting merchants, markets, investors and experts via a single system token.  Here is how it works. The Vestarin team are creating a commission-based platform for e-commerce and entrepreneurialism. The common token creates a form of monetary exchange for customers ‚Äì whether they are shopping for consumer goods or trying to raise funds for their next start-up. All users need to participate in is the system-based token. Further, holders of the token are rewarded by a regular dispersement of income garnered by the commission fees of ongoing platform business.  We recently sat down with Said Radzhabov, the founder of Vestarin to have a chat with him about the project as well as finding out their thoughts and insights.  https://www.chipin.com/vestarin-ceo-said-radzhabov-interview/

Author: VestarinSupport3
Title: [ANN]VESTARINüöÄICO is LIVE |Marketplace of goods and services for cryptocurrency
Body: Thanks for the support, strelok25  On Vestarin you will be able to:  - Purchase goods, services and entertainment for crypto currency.  - Find a team to implement and launch your project.  - Communicate with other crypto-enthusiasts via built-in chat and even transfer coins there.  - Exchange one currency for another in exchange points with the highest reputation, which you can also evaluate.  - Have access to information about emergence and development of new blockchain platforms and opportunities around the world.  - Invest in ICO with minimal risks, based on user rating. Each startup will have its own reputation and feedback from the same crypto-enthusiast users as you, which will help to increase or decrease the credibility of a particular project.  - Become part of the team, if you are keen on a particular structure.  - Integrate your store, restaurant, service or entertainment, earn profit from the platform in the crypto currency.  - Integrate your ICO if it is moderated by Vestarin platform specialists, whose goal is to identify scam and fake projects. After the integration of your ICO, you will be able to attract the attention of the entire community, which will give an opportunity to give life to your project.  - Integrate your exchanger and get leads from the platform.

Title: [ANN]VESTARINüöÄICO is LIVE |Marketplace of goods and services for cryptocurrency
Body: Language problem & solving. Not every user of crypto currency and blockchain technology knows English language. For non-English speakers, it is hard to translate and read the necessary information, because we are still thinking in our native language. Therefore, we decided that the Vestarin platform will be multilingual, so that absolutely everyone would use it comfortably. Thus, you can use the application not only in your country. When traveling, you will always know where you can eat for your crypto money, using geosearch function.  List of languages: English Chinese Korean Japanese Hindi Arabic Spanish Czech German Portuguese Russian Turkish Italian French Polish  You have plenty of languages to choose from

Author: DannyOcean
Title: [ANN]VESTARINüöÄICO is LIVE |Marketplace of goods and services for cryptocurrency
Body: We distribute our profit by the most effective and legal method - redemption (Buy Back and Burn). In other words, we will systematically repatriate VST-tokens from the markets and burn them (i.e. eliminate the tokens). As a result, the number of tokens will decrease, and their value will increase.  Instead of profit distribution we aim at allocating at least 50% funds for the redemption campaign. It`s the optimal practice in the digital economics for the benefit of VST token holders.  We incline to check on legal updates, implement alternative methods of profit distribution according to the rules of the market.  Quote Do you allow other currencies to be used on the marketplace?  You can exchange your currency to VST right on Vestarin platform.

Title: [ANN]VESTARINüöÄICO is LIVE |Marketplace of goods and services for cryptocurrency
Body: It is a complicated smart-contract for that, which include accept from both parties. In two words, when your order has delivered by provider, before carrier will give your order to your hands, you push "delivered" button on your app account, and after he gives your order to you (the same way you usually give a money for your order to carrier). After "delivered" button is confirmed, the deal is done and both parties are happy.
